        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Preliminary Damage Assessment Improvement Act of 20</b><strong>21</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Federal Emergency Management Agency (FEMA) to (1) submit to Congress a report describing the preliminary damage assessment process, as carried out by FEMA in the five years before this bill's enactment; and (2) convene an advisory panel to assist FEMA in improving critical components of that process.</p>]]>
        </text>
